  <brief_title>Effect of Thiamphenicol on EAAT2 and Other Biomarkers From Nasal Biopsied Tissue</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo Controlled, Parallel Group Study to Investigate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Pharmacodynamics of 14-Day Repeated-Dose Administration of Thiamphenicol (RUX 122) in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
